1713→
1714→@layer utilities {
1715→  /* Visually hidden -- accessible to screen readers but not visible.
1716→   * Uses the clip technique for reliable hiding.
1717→   * white-space: nowrap prevents content from being announced as
1718→   * multiple separate items by some screen readers. */
1719→  .visually-hidden,
